{"tid":1067244,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐聯官方：將調查C朗在對陣馬競比賽中的「不當行為」","createTime":"2019-03-18T11:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T09:44:23.000Z","uid":134997,"like":59,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac8be0e9437d97c315cb18aac1c6b42555c1392","tid":1067244,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:36:03.000Z","msg":"歐足聯官方宣佈，將調查C羅在對陣馬競比賽中的&ldquo;不當行為&rdquo;，他在進球后的慶祝動作引發了一定爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在歐冠1/8淘汰賽次回合的比賽中，C羅上演帽子戲法，幫助尤文在首回合兩球告負的情況下完成大逆轉。賽後他模仿馬競主帥西蒙尼之前的動作進行慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐足聯在公告中透露，該事件將在3月21日的會議上得到處理，之後將公佈處罰決定。<br />\n<br />\n《米蘭體育報》在那場比賽後曾報道稱，歐足聯將因為這一動作處罰C羅，他可能被禁賽一場。西蒙尼在兩隊首回合比賽時做出&ldquo;有種&rdquo;的慶祝動作，賽後他因此被罰款2萬歐元，但是沒有被禁賽。"},{"pid":"6cf9ba551ca07d848e641936304baee9059b0d29","tid":1067244,"uid":52087,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:36:51.000Z","msg":"又迫害我朗"},{"pid":"13f8d0312e988e9cf140997d7939d2353172353f","tid":1067244,"uid":196924,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"慢慢查<br />\n如果入到決賽就停鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32edcff96f2c25584d872cfa0cc42af89660a2dc","tid":1067244,"uid":134997,"like":92,"dislike":6,"score":86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ck9MuHb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fck9MuHb.png&h=421d63b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^ C朗女友哭着向歐聯官方求情 兒子在身旁吶喊助威"},{"pid":"f0a95f841a18b8be152f2903a5cbac64be1812a8","tid":1067244,"uid":90515,"like":29,"dislike":7,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:39:39.000Z","msg":"一個雞姦犯仲做啲咁嘅慶祝，好得人驚架"},{"pid":"63ac0a527e409c0a3de4d9a64373e33f0fbecb53","tid":1067244,"uid":134997,"like":56,"dislike":2,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijrGiBf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FijrGiBf.png&h=c214c